{"tid":765302,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有日踢完波坐巴士 開始有d 明白點解巴膠咁中意巴士","createTime":"2018-08-02T15:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T19:45:44.000Z","uid":75139,"like":26,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"48246571211b01033988d2c7b9a655c1a5d5bb2c","tid":765302,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"以前細個好憎坐巴士<br />\n尤其是冷氣巴<br />\n因為個陣d 冷氣巴又臭又逼<br />\n唔知點解嗰陣味會臭到頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前面座位又頂腳(小弟連登仔身高)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧願中意地鐵多d<br />\n<br />\n去到而家坐九巴新車感覺舒服好多<br />\n起碼唔頂腳<br />\n而家d 地鐵又臭又逼又貴又冇位坐<br />\n如果你係調景嶺站上綠色線車<br />\n新既支製車係特別臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係無人臭過有人個陣<br />\n(分係咪支製車好易 見到車廂好新但扶手已經甩緊漆就係支製車)<br />\n馬鐵新車改到得返3個位一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果搭地鐵坐底左又會比人屈讓座 又要嘈一輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇學生優惠之後就盡量唔撚搭地鐵<br />\n而家一攰都係想搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782341de820c259675810c6cce9ce8cd033a8682","tid":765302,"uid":132587,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"九巴新車都舒服<br />\n你平時坐開榴槤?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71013d1c301dbfae7b0a4689dd0b0484091b08c8","tid":765302,"uid":74081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c620e4d69e0159681535c8cff64c63a74dfe3f","tid":765302,"uid":17496,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"坐巴士上層起碼唔洗讓座先"},{"pid":"cd1e19107b115e408b0ca58b25414188be064e22","tid":765302,"uid":9430,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"因為你踢完波臭過架巴士姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.g